message.entry: Constellation length must be a nonzero power of two.
The first dimension of BitTable must be a nonzero power of two.
Inconsistent BitTable specified. The number of columns must be log2() of the number of rows of the BitTable property.
Inconsistent BitTable specified. The row-wise BitTable values must be unique.
Inputs must be either both fixed-size or variable-size signals.
The number of receive antennas of CHAN [: Nt Nr] must be the same as the number of receive antennas of RXSYMBOLS [: Nr].
The number of transmit antennas cannot be greater than the number of receive antennas.
The number of symbols specified by CHAN must be the same as those by RXSymbols.
Constellation and BitTable must have the same number of rows.
